column2: Cricket Ireland, officially the Irish Cricket Union, is the governing body for cricket in Ireland (both the Republic of Ireland and Northern Ireland), and oversees the Ireland cricket team and Ireland women's cricket team.

The India national cricket team, also known as Team India and Men in Blue, represents India in international cricket.
